cs.LG, cs.DC, cs.AI, cs.DS, cs.SE 

This paper is about a machine learning service platform that deals with resource allocation in a multi-tenant scenario. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms), and cs.SE (Software Engineering).
